# Lens Function Buttons

Choose the roles played by the function buttons on the lens (where applicable).

## Lens Function Button Defaults

The default assignments are:

!Lens Function Buttons

- **Lens function button ① Z/F**: ZOOM/FOCUS CONTROL RING
- **Lens function button ② L-Fn1 (rocker zoom button pressed up)**: CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (T)
- **Lens function button ③ L-Fn2 (rocker zoom button pressed down)**: CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (W)

> A XF18-120mmF4 LM PZ WR lens is used here for illustrative purposes.
